(189, 1, '2021-03-05 04:16:00', '2021-03-05 04:16:00', '<p>[vc_row el_id=\"faq_block\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<div class=\"custom_title\">Frequently Asked <b>Questions</b></div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=\"Do you offer free shipping?\" tab_id=\"1614918459257-c73eea26-d8b8\"][vc_column_text]Yes! Although we ship worldwide, we offer free shipping anywhere in the continental US and Canada[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"What gel colors do you have?\" tab_id=\"1614918459264-aa9fef6d-c637\"][vc_column_text]We offer - Blue, Clear, Green, Yellow, Orange, Purple, Pink, And Red.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"How do I pay for the order?\" tab_id=\"1614918562283-f76678a6-6c27\"][vc_column_text]It\'s simple! Click the button below to get 25% off, then choose your product and gel color. Fill out the order form and pay with a credit card and you\'re good to go!<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Where can I find pricing?\" tab_id=\"1614918596166-dd57a24a-3e00\"][vc_column_text]Click the button that says \"Get 25% Off\" and submit your name and email. You\'ll instantly become a member of our wholesale price club and have access to all our pricing.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do you offer refunds on faulty product?\" tab_id=\"1614918624720-64fe23c8-4f26\"][vc_column_text]In the rare event that some of your Gelpax aren\'t what you expected, or if they\'re damaged, we will replace the damaged ones...<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Is there a guarantee?\" tab_id=\"1614918654158-25f78696-399a\"][vc_column_text]We have a 100% risk free guarantee. If you get your custom ice packs and they aren\'t what you were looking for, we will replace them free of charge.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Can you do custom shapes and sizes?\" tab_id=\"1614918675136-32011c5a-dfc7\"][vc_column_text]We specialize in creating custom gel pack products for various applications. Give us a call to discuss your project. We\'re happy to sign an NDA.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"How long does my order take?\" tab_id=\"1614918704287-eab4c884-529f\"][vc_column_text]After payment is accepted and your artwork is approved we produce your order within 10 business days. Then we ship via UPS ground which takes 1-6 business days.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id=\"bottom_subscription\" css=\".vc_custom_1614772114105{background-image: url(http://175.176.184.243:8036/Projects/wordpress/gelpax/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/subs.jpg?id=133) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<div class=\"custom_title\">Be Ready For Anything</div>\r\n<p><span class=\"simple_text\">Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the book.</span><br />\r\n[email-subscribers-form id=\"1\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Faq', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2021-03-05 06:04:16', '2021-03-05 06:04:16', '', 0, 'http://175.176.184.243:8036/Projects/wordpress/gelpax/?page_id=189', 0, 'page', '', 0),
